  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This proposed study will assess the hemodynamic effects and measure the systemic absorption
      of topically applied oxymetazoline in patients undergoing functional endoscopic sinus
      surgery, turbinate surgery, or adenoidectomy. These patients will be receiving oxymetazoline
      as standard of care during the surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
